Title: Inside GitHub Universe: Hosted by Andrea Griffiths & Kedasha Kerr
Description:
Get ready for GitHub Universe 2025! In this special live stream on September 15, Andrea Griffiths and Kedasha Kerr take you behind the scenes of GitHub’s biggest developer event of the year.

We’ll cover:
- The speaker lineup and must-see sessions
- What’s new and exciting at Universe this year
- Tips for getting the most out of the event
- Fun giveaways and community surprises

Whether you’re joining in person or virtually, this preview will help you plan your Universe journey.
Author: GitHub
